{"tid":1627701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修單野，大家幾時先肯明文宣組要做的係文宣唔係割席？","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:14.000Z","uid":23991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa3f414c0b4667b8597a455a60cc562f6872c10","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"裝修除左係令賣港鋪頭冇得做生意同要比錢維修<br />\n最重要的係對準共黨政權 <span style=\"color: red;\">比個好撚強的message全世界聽</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我地要支共同賣港的仆街屎都冇得食</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我承應打中資同賣港鋪之途中<br />\n難免有機會誤中副車 特別係用魔法/有黑警搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157510292609929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157510292609929%26set%3Da.396735049928%26type%3D3%26theater&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=15e04b05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157510292609929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n呢刻就算手足唔裝修都會有黑警去搞事<br />\n無論係黑警定手足做<br />\n和理組應該要做的係搵方法<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">補償被誤中的商戶同認錯道歉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做好個公關<br />\n對準支共同賣港鋪裝修 目標正確 點都唔割<br />\n<br />\n我係垃圾得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇手足一齊幫下手可以點做好個公關<br />\n同岩聽唔該幫我推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce73e7b0764951d096a8f0d1964a9475ac41651","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 <br />\n對準目標 點都唔割"},{"pid":"e5a054f6296597c6c0a7c260c4acd142ac54b3fe","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"驅逐共黨 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a20ac6a6738cb76f337fc477c36d30f01cc2ff0","tid":1627701,"uid":125945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢單野，跟分類做，支持同感謝文宣組。🙏"},{"pid":"bcc640f5b89e7ebf6bbb99fa824a836b3b252d8b","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"希望推得起<br />\n百屌成才<br />\n求指正<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099e9a8ad060d4c623b79e520ed793b32a19c5bf","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a20ac6a6738cb76f337fc477c36d30f01cc2ff0","tid":1627701,"uid":125945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢單野，跟分類做，支持同感謝文宣組。🙏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"跟分類係指？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85b492f88ddabe8dad21d4f463876fdb7e0190d","tid":1627701,"uid":72512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"文宣做野 第一樣首要事係 認同<br />\n<br />\n唔好講割唔割蓆<br />\n<br />\n個文宣自己都唔認同 點去幫你補鑊<br />\n<br />\n今次因為不割蓆 文宣補救隨意裝修<br />\n<br />\n講得誇張D 下次當街輪姦靚女後生藍絲又幫佢地文宣洗底?<br />\n<br />\n過得自己都要過到人呀。兄弟"},{"pid":"15f0100cc6d8289bb0c385fbed7999bd25a531d8","tid":1627701,"uid":236281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1ZhMhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1ZhMhv.jpg&h=128ca870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29bff8e720f1936926cbfec1cb9d0325f9f04ffc","tid":1627701,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85b492f88ddabe8dad21d4f463876fdb7e0190d","tid":1627701,"uid":72512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:26:39.000Z","msg":"文宣做野 第一樣首要事係 認同<br />\n<br />\n唔好講割唔割蓆<br />\n<br />\n個文宣自己都唔認同 點去幫你補鑊<br />\n<br />\n今次因為不割蓆 